definitions.definition: The capital city of and a special municipality of Taiwan , located in the northern part of the island of Taiwan.
A former county of Taiwan , which became New Taipei City.
The government of the Republic of China ( Taiwan ).

main_definition: The capital city of and a special municipality of Taiwan , located in the northern part of the island of Taiwan. [from late 19th c.]
secondary_definitions: A former county of Taiwan , which became New Taipei City. [from 20th c.]
( metonymic ) The government of the Republic of China ( Taiwan ). [from 20th c.]
